Congratulations to Coke Studio for daring to address such an important issue through their exceptional musical talent and for creating a song that resonates deeply with the reality faced by many families. By highlighting the expenses incurred by the bride's family, Coke Studio has given a voice to those who are silently battling societal expectations.  Coke Studio's song serves as a wake-up call, encouraging us to challenge these societal norms and strive for a more equitable and progressive future.
Thank You
